{"tid":277601,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[蘋果又死] iPhone終結者·登場！","createTime":"2017-06-09T17:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T16:47:58.000Z","uid":10495,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77d75beea3203076e8e094cb3500bdfe39745723","tid":277601,"uid":10495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:26:40.000Z","msg":"如今能跟 iPhone 相提並論的大螢幕觸控音樂手機不多，iPhone 已經第三年登上機皇的寶座，難道就沒有一款手機從 iPhone 手裡將機皇的寶座搶回來嗎？ Nokia 大會上最先發佈的這款 Nokia X6 就具備這樣的實力。<br />\n<br />\nNokia X6 有紅黑、藍白兩種顏色可供選擇，該機採用 Symbian OS v9.4 操作系統，基於 S60 5th Edition 平台。X6 的機身厚度只有 13.8mm，相比前作 N97、5800 XpressMusic 都要薄很多，相比 iPhone 還是略厚。另外，X6 能連續播放音樂達 35 小時，與 iPhone 相當。<br />\n<br />\n定位高端市場的 X6，配備 500 萬像素的「卡爾‧蔡司」自動對焦攝頭以及雙 LED 閃光燈，這一點遠勝於 iPhone。X6 有效工作頻率為 433MHz 的中央處理器，以及 32GB 機身存儲空間，與 iPhone 旗鼓相當。不過 X6 省略了 micro SD（T-Flash）存儲卡插槽，同時 1600 萬色、360 x 640 解像度 TFT 觸控螢幕，其面積由 3.5 吋降為 3.2 吋。<br />\n<br />\n另外，X6 還預裝 Ovi 商店，並支援 Come With Music 服務。Ovi 商店是 Nokia 重點打造的商店軟件，儘管目前還比不上 Apple 的 App Store，<span style=\"color: red;\">但是將來全面的 Ovi 服務，將有機會全面超越 App Store。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf57c16c8c2a8733051149527d75e3e779e2bc4","tid":277601,"uid":66351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T19:54:57.000Z","msg":"Elop真偉大，收咗m$(apple?)幾多錢？"},{"pid":"ec644f3dcc4794e03fde4600470d24b0de3468ec","tid":277601,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T20:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSymbian"},{"pid":"a128719b193dcc6e82a49ad7184859986715ebe2","tid":277601,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T20:02:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5148466d60f9d935cc